OL,3,C'A new life': The transformational
OL,4,Cpower of organ transplants
OL,6,FThat was until January 2025, when she
OL,7,Freceived the transplant, which she
OL,8,Fsays has given her "a new lease of
OL,9,Flife".
OL,11,F"I've a lot more energy, I'm not at
OL,12,Fthe hospital as much - I used to go 15
OL,13,Fhours a week, and now I'm down to an
OL,14,Fhour a month.
OL,16,F"It's given me family time, I'm able
OL,17,Fto go on holiday, I can do what I want
OL,18,Fnow," she explains.
