OL,3,C'A new life': The transformational
OL,4,Cpower of organ transplants
OL,6,F"It took 14 years to change my life -
OL,7,Fbut when you're having treatment,
OL,8,Fyou've got no life."
OL,10,FAnna-Marie adds that she'd been on the
OL,11,Ftransplant waiting list so long, she
OL,12,Fhad "lost hope".
OL,14,F"About five years ago, I thought 'I
OL,15,Fdon't think it's ever going to
OL,16,Fhappen'. And obviously, all my worry
OL,17,Fwas that I was going to leave my
OL,18,Fchildren early."
