OL,3,C'A new life': The transformational
OL,4,Cpower of organ transplants
OL,6,FAnna-Marie adds that every day of her
OL,7,F"new" life is a gift.
OL,9,F"I'm still emotional now - I get days
OL,10,Fthat I get up and I'm like 'Is this
OL,11,Freal?' and now it's a new life - a new
OL,12,Fbeginning."
OL,14,FKesley agrees, "It's like I had a new
OL,15,Fmum - and I know that sounds like a
OL,16,Fcliche, because it's only the kidney -
OL,17,Fbut everything changed for her."
