OL,3,C'A new life': The transformational
OL,4,Cpower of organ transplants
OL,6,FHaving spent so many years in and out
OL,7,Fof hospital waiting for the life-
OL,8,Fchanging procedure, Anna-Marie is
OL,9,Furging islanders to have the necessary
OL,10,Fconversations with their families - so
OL,11,Fthat if the worst does happen, they
OL,12,Fknow what to do.
OL,14,F"I would like to tell people to please
OL,15,Fdonate their organs because it does
OL,16,Fchange lives," she says.
OL,18,F"Those organs are very important for
OL,19,Fpeople, especially in Jersey, because
OL,20,Feverything has to go through the UK."
