OL,3,C'A new life': The transformational
OL,4,Cpower of organ transplants
OL,6,FSamantha North, one of Jersey's Senior
OL,7,FNurses for practice assurance,
OL,8,Fexplains that despite Jersey changing
OL,9,Fto an opt-out system for organ
OL,10,Fdonation in 2019, it's still vital
OL,11,Fthat people have the difficult
OL,12,Fconversations with their families so
OL,13,Fthat everyone is prepared.
OL,15,FWhilst attitudes and practicalities
OL,16,Fhave changed, she believes "the
OL,17,Fconversation is the most crucial part
OL,18,Fof the process".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
